{"tid":698347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神級轉field】龜公轉做喃嘸師傅 陳達仁：無道德變有道德","createTime":"2018-06-11T15:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T14:47:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfdc9a6b2e4696f8ce5de8a432d3af9191d08e6","tid":698347,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8JDmCEBodns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8JDmCEBodns&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3v6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7db4ee0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8JDmCEBodns</a><br />\n<br />\n陳達仁由沒有道德的龜公，轉做超渡亡魂、功德無量的殯儀喃嘸師傅，反差很大，不過他的擔心很短暫，因為每晚做完法事仍要陪老細，繼續做龜公。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說當年他向殯儀業鉅子要求轉field，希望試試堂倌角色。堂倌即是靈堂司儀，高呼：「有客到，一鞠躬、再鞠躬、三鞠躬。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳達仁自忖應付得來，殯儀鉅子卻安排他做喃嘸師傅，原來該殯儀館規模大，領導層分工，鉅子雖是話事人，卻不直接管理堂倌，法事部則是他的baby。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳生也真上進，當時上學不斷，他說：「我仍然繼續努力學業，在所有人面前包裝成好學生，讀書代表有前途；晚上做喃嘸師傅，代表學一門手藝；最後做擦鞋仔（及龜公），建立人際關係。整件事是健康的！」簡直一日滿足三個願望啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喃嘸師傅肚裡經文不少，陳達仁初學乍練，要加把勁，他卻染上賭博陋習，月頭捧着工資去澳門呼么喝六，還老定地買了次日回程船票，滿擬贏大錢，當晚消夜直落，次日方歸，然而半小時不到便輸光，灰頭土臉回到碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那一刻小子發誓戒賭，發奮讀書，讀的卻是經書，他就坐在碼頭苦讀，悲憤之下所學甚快。下個月他又賭過，又輸光，又戒賭讀經，如此輸得幾次，所知經文已不少，已經可以出場。"},{"pid":"a70c4e19d7ef06e71a77e51462893fe6343f623d","tid":698347,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180602/590306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180602%2F590306&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3v6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=54c61e69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180602%2F590306&h=dc364a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180602/590306</a>"},{"pid":"ce83a0c65f1dcb393840043aaec200f42d48e3b3","tid":698347,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f66fed8010f5a6d89a6eecfaa957fc72ee3b858","tid":698347,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17aec0076af50d8dbeb492bb4e5384b58ee7f57","tid":698347,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc4eb99e2914de611e9c4fa4153b9350232c059","tid":698347,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}